        <qualifiedname>bt_cap_initiator_broadcast_create_param::broadcast_code</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>16-octet broadcast code. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Only valid if <computeroutput>encrypt</computeroutput> is true.</para>
<para>If the value is a string or a the value is less than 16 octets, the remaining octets shall be 0.</para>
<para>Example: The string &quot;Broadcast Code&quot; shall be [42 72 6F 61 64 63 61 73 74 20 43 6F 64 65 00 00] </para>
        </detaileddescription>
